import { Box, Button, defaultProps, Tab, Tabs } from 'grommet';
import React from 'react';
import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom";


function TabsForm() {

    let history = useHistory();

    return(
        <>

        <Box gap="large">
            <Button onClick={() => history.goBack()}>  Back</Button>
        </Box>
            
            <Box direction="row" alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'medium' }} pad="medium" gap="small">
            <Box gap="large">
                <Button onClick={() => history.goBack()}>  Back</Button>
            </Box>
                
                <Tabs>
                    <Tab title="Procurement Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 1</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Forwarder Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 2</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="CHA Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 3</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Supplier & Product Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 4</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Customs Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 5</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Invoice Remittance Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 6</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Asset-grave Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 7</Box>
                    </Tab>
                </Tabs>
            </Box>
        </>
    );
}

export default TabsForm;
